description: Removes tags from the resource with the specified ARN.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the resource to be untagged. The ARN must be URL-encoded.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: Array of tag keys (strings) for the tags to be removed. See Best practices and strategies in Tagging AWS Resources and Tag Editor for details, including restrictions that apply to tags and 'Tag naming limits and requirements'; Amazon IVS has no constraints on tags beyond what is documented there. (string) ---
